PRIVACY NOTICE

This application collects and processes user data as described in the
application's Privacy Policy and Terms of Service. By using this application,
you agree to the collection and use of information in accordance with these
policies.

Data collected may include:
- Bird detection and observation data
- Location information (with user permission)
- Photos and images (with user permission)
- Usage analytics (anonymized)

Users have the right to:
- Access their data
- Export their data
- Request data deletion
- Opt out of data sharing programs

For more information, see the Privacy Policy section in the application
settings or visit the project's GitHub repository.

